BBCalc 0.8
==========

Major changes:

	* Application has been completely rewritten from wxPython to PyGTK

	* All source code went through a big refactoring

	* License has been upgraded to GPL version 3


New features:

	* Preferences dialog box (support GConf), allow to select default 'system of
	measurement' and 'gender'

	* Generic help system (Gnome)

	* New calculators: BMI, Calorie Burning: Running, Weight Units Converter


Translation changes:

  	* updated: Russian


Minor changes:

	* A lot of other small changes... :)